{"tid":1693147,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律師會會長：疑犯被捕　律政司應盡快決定檢控與否","createTime":"2019-11-04T12:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T12:55:12.000Z","uid":142878,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7084f4b80136c8d2dae8f437a4362f0907e42a","tid":1693147,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】反修例運動至今逾二千人被捕，但檢控數字相對較低，香港律師會會長彭韻僖指，疑犯被捕後，律政司應盡快決定檢控與否，以維持公眾對法治的信心。<br />\n<br />\n香港律師會會長<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">彭韻僖</span></strong>：「警方作出逮捕後，我們希望律政司盡快研究案情，檢視是否適合提出訴訟，盡快經過法庭程序，才能令香港朋友對我們的法治有信心。很多人都應該聽過，如果法治很慢都不能彰顯，我們一直都說Justice delayed(遲來的公義)，即Justice denied(不是公義)。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=368684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368684&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=f4fada17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368684&h=674a2e20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=368684</a>"},{"pid":"54bf8c0d58ce577c4f7f66919a4aeabf5677c477","tid":1693147,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"信報<br />\n今日 15:34 時事脈搏<br />\n<br />\n律師會:盡快決定是否起訴免影響對法治信心<br />\n<br />\n放大圖片<br />\n反修例運動持續近4個月，逾2000人被捕，當中只有少數人被控告，律師會會長彭韻僖認為檢控當局應盡快研究各案件，決定是否起訴，以免影響社會對香港法治的信心。<br />\n<br />\n彭韻僖指現時警察拘捕多人，望律政司儘快研究案情，評估是否合適提訴，再由法庭處理，如果涉案人士遲遲未能由法庭處理，「Justice delay係justice denied」，惟有律政司從速決定檢控與否，再由法庭審訊可檢控的案件，才能令香港人對法治有信心。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\ninRead invented by Teads<br />\n對於市民一直堅持成立獨立調查委員會徹查反修例事件，彭韻僖認為現時社會有大衝擊、衝突，需要有一個獨立委員會全面調查，但是否需要成立獨立調查委員會，則未明言，僅指「有好多唔同方式都做到」。<br />\n<br />\n至於有聲音質疑法庭就屬違法的事情批出臨時禁制令的合理性，她指法庭審訊中，現非適合評論階段。<br />\n<br />\n早前大律師公會致函警務處處長指律師接觸被捕人士有困難，甚至受警員辱罵，彭韻僖未回應律師會曾否收到相關會員提出的個案，但指會與大律師公會緊密聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n至於曾任律師會理事的立法會議員何君堯早前被投訴有操守問題，律師會早前表明會跟進，彭韻僖指按機制，成立委員會處理，會按程序調查，曾與何君堯共事的理事不會參與，預計至少數月處理，結果按需要公布。<br />\n<br />\n律師會在月底將會舉行活動，邀請多名中學生一同探討中、港、澳三地司法制度之別，希望年輕一代多了解不同地方法治核心，了解各地司法制度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2293629/%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83%3A%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E5%85%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%B0%8D%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2293629%2F%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%259C%2583%253A%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%2585%258D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25BF%2583&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=4b501807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2293629/%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83%3A%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E5%85%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%B0%8D%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83</a>"},{"pid":"0b9d6d71f4f2a4feb177d7905f2633cbbc48975a","tid":1693147,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"RTHK<br />\n<br />\n彭韻僖：警方拘捕疑犯後 律政司應盡快決定是否起訴<br />\n2019-11-04 HKT 14:42<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彭韻僖：警方拘捕疑犯後 律政司應盡快決定是否起訴<br />\n反修例引發的抗議持續，示威者與警方使用的暴力升級。香港律師會會長彭韻僖出席活動，被問到會否譴責警方暴力時說，任何一方的暴力都不應容許。她又說，警方拘捕疑犯後，律政司應該盡快決定是否起訴，再到法庭審訊，因為「遲來的公義，等同否定公義」。<br />\n<br />\n彭韻僖又說，香港現時面對大型衝突，需要全面研究事情如何發生，有需要成立一個有獨立性的委員會調查。至於是否贊成成立社會普遍要求的「獨立調查委員會」，她說，外國有很多不同方法值得研究，舉例指倫敦2011年騷亂，民間有英國《衛報》及倫敦經濟學院，就聯合進行獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489987-20191104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489987-20191104.htm&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=66281261\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489987-20191104.htm&h=b54e8532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489987-20191104.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0ef594ca6cb5f3667c923234dfbb9c7cbb76d733","tid":1693147,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"律師會不嬲藍 <br />\nSolit會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大律師公會先正常"},{"pid":"a6dd67279cb5cf35de20550c3daefeffd9304e56","tid":1693147,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"HK01<br />\n【逃犯條例】律師會會長：律政司應盡快決定是否起訴被捕者<br />\n<br />\n政情<br />\n<br />\n撰文：羅家晴<br />\n2019-11-04 15:40<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-11-04 18:47<br />\n<br />\n反修例運動持續不斷，香港律師會會長彭韻僖今（4日）會見傳媒時表示，雖然現時本港法治受到衝擊，但她仍然對法治有信心，強調不少人都認同法律和法治的重要性，希望每人都應岀一份力維護法治。<br />\n<br />\n對於警方最近拘捕大量示威者，但檢控數字較低，彭韻僖認為，檢控由律政司負責，希望律師司能盡快研究案情，檢視案情是否適合提岀訴訟，「遲來的公義等同否定公義」，不要影響香港人對法治的信心。<br />\n<br />\n律師會會長彭韻僖(中)表示，警方拘捕疑犯後，律政司應該盡快決定是否起訴。(羅家晴攝)<br />\n律師會會長彭韻僖(中)表示，警方拘捕疑犯後，律政司應該盡快決定是否起訴。(羅家晴攝)<br />\n<br />\n彭韻僖今日出席活動後，被問到會否譴責警方暴力，她稱律師會在三個月來已六次發聲明，重申任何一方使用暴力都是絕不容許。對於成立獨立調查委員會(COI)，彭韻僖稱有必要全面檢視及研究反修例風波的發生及未來方向，認為應有一個獨立性的委員會；至於是否成立COI，她稱有不同方法，如英國倫敦2011年騷亂後，成立「騷亂、社區及受害者委員會」。<br />\n<br />\n有市民早前向律師會投訴，指立法會議員何君堯涉嫌違反《律師執業規則》，彭韻僖稱任何投訴都會跟現有機制處理，由委員會跟進，而所有與何君堯共事過的理事將不會牽涉在內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，律師會今年第十年舉行「青Teen講場」，今次主題為「三司有法」，將探討香港、內地及澳門的社會的道德及法理異同。律師會理事湯文龍指三地關係密切，希望學生從活動中學習法律知識，屆時將談及電子煙、「Part time girl friend」等議題，預料會800至1000名學生參加。"},{"pid":"116214c6d4f0d838c7ae3c41185880eda9dc8231","tid":1693147,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:25:51.000Z","msg":"政府唔夠人調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801a6e4b257f8d9d087309445b8fd58f38e16291","tid":1693147,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:26:51.000Z","msg":"appledaily<br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】律師會會長未撐獨立調查　<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拒表明公開投訴何君堯的調查結果</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191104/60229577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191104%2F60229577&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=1fa8d3f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191104%2F60229577&h=8feed810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191104/60229577</a>"},{"pid":"67452184a0eb88efbd9b42877e6a8ce1f89f1379","tid":1693147,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200f248f77fea0f3ba209fab0d544637bba74237","tid":1693147,"uid":175668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"好多律師藍底"},{"pid":"c69353d53d6f09c5cd4e8cf207f87bbc3f7b992e","tid":1693147,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"潛台詞係咪<br />\n「唔起訴就放人」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5434396223bba777a62f13c5ca3878091337997","tid":1693147,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"116214c6d4f0d838c7ae3c41185880eda9dc8231","tid":1693147,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:25:51.000Z","msg":"政府唔夠人調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"咁咪放囉<br />\n拖佢老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5af9f9fb7712aa5dba59763b1dbc45dec46637","tid":1693147,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:28:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d13a51e8c9eece2e75e3c428cce0c9b5fd96bbe","tid":1693147,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"點解唔覺有撐警團體送野畀律師會會長ge新聞ge?<br />\n阿會長你係咪撐警撐得唔夠勁?<br />\n無人識你wo家陣<br />\n<br />\n同樣做律師會會長<br />\n何君堯叻過你多多聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c43f90f55622b68143c0ee510e6b4c8f9b19026","tid":1693147,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c69353d53d6f09c5cd4e8cf207f87bbc3f7b992e","tid":1693147,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"潛台詞係咪<br />\n「唔起訴就放人」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"佢係想起訴哂咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1affb63b39b1691df9d48012d399d0406ad61ef8","tid":1693147,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:30:13.000Z","msg":"唔通班律師會公開講支持暴力咩<br />\n兩邊都顯責<br />\n算係噉"},{"pid":"a7cba9f42e262a37f68fcd8f0e65ebc5f131117d","tid":1693147,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:33:34.000Z","msg":"律師會會長,藍底喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1562fe70b4ade9552a795712e5705ac6ca67a577","tid":1693147,"uid":152387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:42:44.000Z","msg":"何君堯嗰PART姑且唔講<br />\n盡快決定檢控與否,呢樣嘢唔覺有咩問題喎<br />\n畢竟拖成幾年先檢控對所有被捕人士都係好大嘅精神負擔<br />\n而且會造成寒蟬效應,怕出位怕得罪政府陣營而被檢控"},{"pid":"fe1c798e205f2e384b8e188f1c6fc57282c42343","tid":1693147,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1562fe70b4ade9552a795712e5705ac6ca67a577","tid":1693147,"uid":152387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:42:44.000Z","msg":"何君堯嗰PART姑且唔講<br />\n盡快決定檢控與否,呢樣嘢唔覺有咩問題喎<br />\n畢竟拖成幾年先檢控對所有被捕人士都係好大嘅精神負擔<br />\n而且會造成寒蟬效應,怕出位怕得罪政府陣營而被檢控"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"16年個堆好多去到19年仲告緊,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}